vendorName: NATTIQ - IT SERVICES CANADA INC. NATTIQ
extraDescription: This contract is related to the implementation of the new request for reconsideration (for Employment Insurance) and appeal process (Social Security Tribunal) for the Employment Insurance, Canada Pension and Old Age Security programs. The purpose of this contract is to assist the Department in a review of current governance, accountabilities and roles and responsibilities as they relate to reconsideration and appeal processing within programs areas and to develop and implement business architecture and change management approach that provides for increased alignment, efficiency and is cost effective.
